<br>
Yes, our goal is to get into Sleeper's.  However, we have yet to be done with:<br>
<br>
Velketor (we've failed like 7 times)<br>
The Dain<br>
Yelinak<br>
85% of ToV<br>
Phara Dar (yes, we're nowhere near done with VP and it looks like we're the only ones still planning on going there)<br>
PoG (although, this zone sucks)<br>
etc.<br>
<br>
