<br>
So I guess what I'm saying is, if some of the higher level guilds, like SR, are only interested in the big mobs, why can't they at least bring some lower people...strangers (/gasp) to gain experience from them and some of the old planar armor?  I have signed up for more SR raids over the last year than I can remember and never been picked.  Skyre Draneth is the only large guild that has ever taken me (several times /thank Skyre).  <p><DIV ALIGN="center">
